                "title": "Contains Firmware"
            },
            {
                "category": "details",
                "text": "NBU:NBU",
                "title": "Product Team"
            },
            {
                "category": "summary",
                "text": "To protect your system, download and install the latest NVIDIA components from the links provided in this document.",
                "title": "Summary"
            },
            {
                "category": "details",
                "text": "The issues are relevant to users on the local host with VF access. For deployments that do not use VF or do not host untrusted tenants (e.g. Storage use cases, AI/HPC factory use cases), the vulnerabilities would only be accessible to privileged users (admin, hypervisor, etc.).<br><div>On ConnectX-8 devices, there are additional security mitigations that limit exploitation. A successful exploit would require another vulnerability on the system to bypass those security mechanisms. For this reason we consider the CVSS score for ConnectX-8 as 8.0 High, <a href=\"https://www.first.org/cvss/calculator/3-1#CVSS:3.1/AV:A/AC:H/PR:L/UI:N/S:C/C:H/I:H/A:H\">AV:A/AC:H/PR:L/UI:N/S:C/C:H/I:H/A:H</a>.<br></div><div><br></div>",
                "title": "Mitigation Notes"
            },
            {
                "category": "details",
                "text": "<div><span style=\"color: var(--text-color-primary); font-family: var(--psirt-font-family-sans);\">* These products are only affected by CVE-2025-23351.</span></div><div><span style=\"color: var(--text-color-primary); font-family: var(--psirt-font-family-sans);\">Firmware download links:</span><br><ul><li>ConnectX-5 - <a href=\"https://network.nvidia.com/support/firmware/connectx5en/\">https://network.nvidia.com/support/firmware/connectx5en/</a></li><li>ConnectX-6 De FW -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://network.nvidia.com/support/firmware/connectx6de/\">https://network.nvidia.com/support/firmware/connectx6de/</a></li><li>ConnectX-6 Dx FW -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://network.nvidia.com/support/firmware/connectx6dx/\">https://network.nvidia.com/support/firmware/connectx6dx/</a></li><li>ConnectX-6 Lx FW -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://network.nvidia.com/support/firmware/connectx6lx/\">https://network.nvidia.com/support/firmware/connectx6lx/</a></li><li>ConnectX-7 FW -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://network.nvidia.com/support/firmware/connectx7/\">https://network.nvidia.com/support/firmware/connectx7/</a></li><li>ConnectX-8 FW -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://network.nvidia.com/support/firmware/connectx8/\">https://network.nvidia.com/support/firmware/connectx8/</a></li></ul>These issues were found internally.</div>",
                "title": "Bulletin Notes"
            },
